<div
  id="blog-banner"
  class="h-12 flex justify-center items-center md:bg-neutral-600/20 bg-neutral-600 border-white/10 gap-2 group md:relative fixed bottom-0 inset-x-0 z-20"
>
  <a href="https://cristianblog.vercel.app">
    <span class="absolute z-20 -inset-y-1 -inset-x-1"></span>
  </a>
  <span class="font-semibold text-sm text-amber-100/90 hidden md:block">
    Ven a visitar mi blog, hablo sobre tecnologia, dise√±o y mas temas que te
    pueden interesar.
  </span>
  <span class="font-semibold text-sm text-amber-100/90 md:hidden">
